{"type": "article", "id": 25250, "title": "Prada利润大跌，以及，丝芙兰和迪士尼合作彩妆系列｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-04-11T09:23:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}, {"id": 360, "name": "app"}, {"id": 26046, "name": "美妆产品"}, {"id": 23146, "name": "杂志封面"}, {"id": 11180, "name": "海滩"}, {"id": 341, "name": "运动"}, {"id": 3126, "name": "牛仔"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 26047, "name": "Porsche"}, {"id": 1508, "name": "Net-a-porter"}, {"id": 1081, "name": "丝芙兰"}, {"id": 111, "name": "迪士尼"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607132429NZALH6lKSwP1BF8v.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/beauty-features/covergirl-beauty-app-10406284/\"><b>Cover Girl 推出首个美妆 APP</b></a>｜Cover Girl 也开始进入蓬勃的美妆 app 市场，推出了首个美妆 APP——BeautyU，除了增强现实技术，还有个性化推荐的功能。对此，宝洁公司全球美妆部门执行副总裁 Eggleston Bracey 表示“目标是让化妆变简单，同时购买也随之步骤简化”，希望借此提高美妆产品线上和线下的销量。Go-Globe 预计到 2017 年全世界的移动 app 收益将达到 770 亿美元，美妆类 app 也成为了美妆品牌寻求突破、更好进入市场的主要方式之一。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Dame-Vivienne-Westwood-to-release-diaries,679801.html\"><b>Vivienne Westwood 将出版日记</b></a>｜英国最有影响力的设计师之一 Vivienne Westwood 近日宣布将出版新书 <i>Get a Life</i>，集结了过去的一些日记，预计今年 10 月 6 日上市。她本人表示：“我的日记涉及到我关心的事情，不仅仅是时尚，也是艺术、写作、人权、气候变化和自由。我把这些称之为<i> Get a Life </i>因为这就是我的感受——你必须参与其中、畅所欲言并且采取行动。”<br></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/China-weakness-drives-Prada-quarterly-profit-down-27-pct,679486.html\"><b>中国市场疲软致使 Prada 季度利润下跌 27%</b></a>｜意大利奢侈品牌 Prada 近日财报显示季度利润下跌了 27%，主要由于中国地区死气沉沉的市场表现。并且 Prada 表示因为动荡的经济环境而不确定未来国际奢侈品市场的预期。截至 1 月 31 日的三个月内，Prada 获得了 9580 万欧元（约合 1.089 亿美元）的净收入，去年同期则达到 1.314 亿欧元。考虑到人民币的疲软，和香港差劲的市场表现，截至 1 月 31 日，Prada 的全年净收入则从 4.507 亿欧元跌至 3.309 亿。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/-Forever-21-to-close-flagship-store-in-Scotland,679513.html\"><b>Forever 21 退出苏格兰市场</b></a>｜美国快时尚品牌 Forever 21 近日宣布关闭位于格拉斯哥的苏格兰旗舰店，这也是 Forever 21  在苏格兰唯一的一家店。2013 年 5 月开业，三层占地 6.1 万平方英尺的店铺未来将由 H&amp;M 占领。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2016/focus/athletic-outdoor/adidas-porsche-design-sport-ultra-boost-sneakers-release-210544/\"><b>Adidas 与保时捷团队合作的  Ultra Boost 版将上市</b></a>｜Adidas 自去年二月首次发布 Ultra Boost 跑鞋后，赢得广泛关注。与保时捷运动设计团队（Porsche Design Sport）的限量合作 Ultra Boost  系列将在 4 月 15 日上市，350 美元一双。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132414jUqJTlKP74F8LWo6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132414dKZ38A9NB76PlHXa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p>维秘天使 Alessandra Ambrosio 在沙滩上身穿一些运动感的时装，<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/alessandra-ambrosio-sporty-looks-edit/\">为奢侈品电商 Net-a-Porter 的杂志 The Edit （四月刊</a>）拍摄封面：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132415zfrqxF1EtaiSHM8y.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132415nx34GU2vdHEAfIC6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132416nVh9Gse8Z4Rv7Kw0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64191729\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132416Yjchre6TuD1V3p2d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">Tommy Hilfiger <a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/04/10/tommy-jeans-2016-campaign/#slide-3\">2016 的牛仔系列</a>找来了 Lucky Blue Smith 和 Hailey Baldwin 来拍广告，充满怀旧的 90 年代气息：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132417qcWwngIs4L3yJ0uf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132417gos1mjFPhMAkI5H9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132418DO1b4Q5p8ukIzexj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.17625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071324180Le5whn43i9J8Dto.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p>姐妹档 Kendall Jenner 与 Kylie Jenner 此前推出“Kendall + Kylie”系列迅速售罄，最近<a href=\"http://www.neimanmarcus.com/en-hk/Kendall-Kylie/Designers/cat57940749/c.cat\">与时尚电商 Neiman Marcus 又推出联名系列服装</a>，已经上市。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132419zxlROcIyJaA7Vb9T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713241925PCKnbaEY34oRJW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132420Zg4FEPHOM3CDT0J6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">丝芙兰与迪士尼的最新合作，是<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/sephora-minnie-mouse-disney-makeup-buy/\">以 Minnie Mouse 为灵感的彩妆产品</a>。金色外观，点缀圆点和米妮的蝴蝶结图案。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132420Y3L065WKNvrjdeTt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">眼线笔／化妆镜</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132421D7Hc6SkjXhuaIJ04.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">粉盒／唇彩</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132421JyYEPTD7jNGb5Vkc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">美妆刷套装／腮红 </div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132422PaQXrWmsMUG3nlSH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">眼影盘／口红</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">宝马为庆祝成立 100 周年，为日本市场推出 40 台<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/bmw-i3-carbonight\"> i3 Carbonight 特别版</a>，售价 5.5 万美元：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132422Rb3ahOLGUk5HwyJd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071324235eHdBtzcSopLMahv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132423euJvRWL9tZqNPn3x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132424rEJOaBo53hCKWwyi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071324246JR0a2ITY4ZEAQGC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"> Kristen Stewart 为 Chanel 拍摄了一组名为<a href=\"http://bae.hypebeast.com/2016/4/kristen-stewart-chanel-paris-in-rome-campaign\"> “Paris in Rome” 的大片</a>，充满撩人气质，Karl Lagerfeld 掌镜。</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132425GUVu7CWmYIbder5k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132426Spmb0RoJCzGKrMUL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132426XymN1GFBZRYE0p27.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">H&amp;M 发布了今夏的<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/hm-summer-2016-outfits/\">搭配指南“New Ease”</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132427QyglWtcDFRsnTM48.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132427bwBrqM796CUVK4Am.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132427TMxGU7hnIH9JP3ag.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132428P2hvXEcYSJLmDbCB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132428to4iLzBemRY2d7vX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n\n"}